## 10. RISK ASSESSMENT

| Risk | Probability | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|-------------|--------|------------|
| Absorption targets have unexpected unique code | Medium | Medium | Clone first, assess before deleting |
| BytePort unmerged feature branches conflict with main | Low | Medium | Branch audit before any changes |
| Network unavailable for GH cloning | Low | High | Use any cached data; document limitation |
| phenotype-infra pkgs diverge from source repos | Low | Medium | Unify as L2 priority |
| SOTA research in nanovms SPEC.md becomes stale | Medium | Low | L4-007 scheduled refresh |
| 71-pillar grading reveals previously unknown gaps | Medium | Medium | Include in DAG as auditing step |

